  "prompt": "Is Star Wars: The Old Republic for Mac?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, Star Wars: The Old Republic (SWTOR) is primarily designed for Windows. However, Mac users can still play the game by using compatibility software such as Boot Camp, which allows Windows applications to run on Mac hardware. Additionally, some players have had success using virtualization software like Parallels Desktop or running it through Wine, though these methods may have varying levels of performance and stability. \n\nFor the most current information, I recommend checking the official SWTOR website or relevant forums for any updates regarding Mac support.",
